column2: SELECT     o.apogee_id,m.ra_epoch2# AS ra1, m.dec_epoch2# AS dec1,     o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2,   mode =#, type=# into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.Dani_table_Chiara AS m  CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra_epoch2#, m.dec_epoch2#, #) AS n      JOIN apogeeObject AS o ON n.objid=o.apogee_id
